nodes.text: Leeni was a female wokling who lived around the time of the Battle of Endor.

Leeni was one of six 8-inch plush woklings made by Kenner. While the characters of Malani, Nippet, and Wiley were established in the Ewoks television series, Mookiee, Leeni, and Gwig have yet to be identified in a particular source.
